OL,3,CSNP tells Bank of England the 'time is
OL,4,Cnow right' for interest rate cut
OL,6,FThe Bank's Monetary Policy Committee
OL,7,Fmeets eight times a year to set the UK
OL,8,Fbase rate, which then influences the
OL,9,Finterest rates applied to mortgages,
OL,10,Floans and savings accounts, among
OL,11,Fother things.
OL,13,FWith the next meeting scheduled to
OL,14,Ftake place on Thursday June 20, two
OL,15,Fweeks before voters go to the polls in
OL,16,Fthe General Election, Mr Hosie said
OL,17,Ffamilies struggling after rises in
OL,18,Fmortgage payments, food and energy
OL,19,Fbills "need help now".
