OL,3,CSNP tells Bank of England the 'time is
OL,4,Cnow right' for interest rate cut
OL,6,FMr Hosie said Rishi Sunak's party had
OL,7,F"trashed the economy and have sent the
OL,8,Fcost of living in the UK soaring", as
OL,9,Fhe said it was important to "get rid
OL,10,Fof the Tory government and put
OL,11,FScotland's interests first".
OL,13,FThe former SNP depute leader added:
OL,14,F"The fact is, Scottish families are
OL,15,Fpaying too high a price for
OL,16,FWestminster failure. The cost of
OL,17,Fmortgages, food, and energy bills have
OL,18,Fgone through the roof and families
OL,19,Fneed help now."
