OL,3,CSNP tells Bank of England the 'time is
OL,4,Cnow right' for interest rate cut
OL,6,FHe continued: "It is possible for
OL,7,Fpoliticians to fully respect the
OL,8,Findependence of the central bank
OL,9,Fwhilst also telling the public what we
OL,10,Fbelieve.
OL,12,F"The SNP believes the Bank of England
OL,13,Fshould begin to help fix this Tory
OL,14,Fmess by lowering interest rates, to
OL,15,Freduce the cost of mortgages and give
OL,16,Fhard-hit Scottish families a break.
OL,18,F"We believe the time is now right to
OL,19,Ffollow the lead of our European
OL,20,Fneighbours and reduce rates to help
OL,21,Fstruggling households."
