OL,3,CSNP tells Bank of England the 'time is
OL,4,Cnow right' for interest rate cut
OL,6,FCriticising both Labour and the
OL,7,FConservatives, Mr Hosie said: "Brexit
OL,8,FBritain is broken and neither Rishi
OL,9,FSunak or Sir Keir Starmer can fix it,
OL,10,Fwhen they are both wedded to Brexit
OL,11,Fand austerity cuts, hammering the
OL,12,Feconomy, the NHS, and family incomes.
OL,14,F"In contrast, the SNP will always put
OL,15,FScotland's interests first and stand
OL,16,Fup for Scottish families against
OL,17,FWestminster austerity cuts and Brexit."
